	&lt;li&gt;
		Venkatesh J. revised October 28 2007. An Introduction to Total Productive Maintenance (TPM) http://www.plantmaintenance.com/articles/tpm_intro.shtml&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/reliability-centered_maintenance/~4/ldmqiOM0t8U" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
